cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with deep learning architecture for classification and detection in mammograms, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of weak supervision is also a key aspect of the paper, which could potentially fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves the localization of different types of findings in full resolution.
